Class SafeOrderedObjectMessageStatistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.admin.SafeOrderedObjectMessageStatistics
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.guidewire.pl.system.service.data.Idable, Serializable

    public class SafeOrderedObjectMessageStatistics
extends Object
implements com.guidewire.pl.system.service.data.Idable, Serializable
    Data object used to encapsulate messaging statistics for messages related to a particular "ordering object" (such as a claim).

      • canRetry

        boolean canRetry()
        Returns:
        true if there are messages to retry (should only be one) and there aren't any failed ones. Returns false otherwise.

      • canSkip

        boolean canSkip()
        Returns:
        true if there are any messages that can be skipped. False otherwise.
